  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "energy_consumption")
  |> group(columns: ["location"])
  |> count()' \
  --org energyorg \
  --token YOUR_API_TOKEN_HERE
Expected Result: Should show count of records ingested per location.

Verify Threshold Detection
